column2: PAPA BEAR THIS IS ALPHA BLACK. I HAVE CONDUCTED THE RECON OF NORTHERN PART OF THE AIRBASE. OVER.
ROGER ALPHA BLACK, PROCEED TO THE SOUTHERN PART. OVER.
PAPA BEAR THIS IS ALPHA BLACK. I HAVE NOW LOCATED IN THE SOUTHERN PART OF THE AIRBASE. OVER.
COPY THAT ALPHA, PROCEED TO THE EXTRACTION POINT AND COME HOME. OVER.
